{"tid":230519,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊濾水器公司，深入睇濾芯材料","createTime":"2017-05-05T12:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-12T10:21:42.000Z","uid":80396,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3c19d4fe1dce78094d4eba6196787af85b9c639","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:05:49.000Z","msg":"字面意思，深入睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次會睇三種最常見既濾水材料，三種都係係市面買得到而又常見既。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/r92tcdq6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fr92tcdq6&h=d65a423e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先要講下濾水器既原理。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n濾水器主要有兩個原理，「吸附」「隔除」<br />\n<br />\n吸附即係利用物料本身既特性，將污染身吸住。<br />\n<br />\n隔除即係用物料本身既密度，阻隔水中既固體污染物。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地從5蚊銀開始睇，拎個放大概念先中。<br />\n<br />\n自己比錢買，畫質低，張就下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5蚊銀:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pczsudfi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpczsudfi&h=0a2fb8ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n搭車買野必備，其兄弟有各種紙幣，係人類耗盡一生既目標。<br />\n<br />\n表面乾淨實際係好污糟，所以記住常洗手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n活性碳+交換樹脂：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qs9f672a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqs9f672a&h=c895b216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最常見都係最大路既物料。原理係利用活性碳同交換樹脂所總成既密度去阻隔污染，同時本身都會吸附污染物既作用。一般會加入銀離子壓抑細菌。<br />\n<br />\n相中可見佢係密度最低既物料。但佢既特點係「吸附」，所以即使密度一般係0.5微米，都有一定效能。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n矽藻瓷：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pyzvl9ex\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpyzvl9ex&h=9f102fb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國道頓最常見既物料。密度會比碳濾芯高，一般係0.5至0.1微米，可以隔除更多固體污染物。一般會加入銀離子壓抑細菌。<br />\n<br />\n佢既特點係密，但得個密字係冇用，所以某D會配合活性碳同交換樹脂一齊用。因為佢既密度高，所以佢係需要定期刷下，以保持水壓穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中空絲膜：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fnxbc5si\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffnxbc5si&h=4ca94eb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本水龍頭式濾水器既常客。密度最高，一般係0.1微米。可以有效隔除固體污染物同某D細菌。但絕少會配合活性碳+交換樹脂，所以係處理重金屬方面會比較弱。亦因為佢密度高，所以壽命會比較短，要換得比較密。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外有一粒叫。。能量石之類：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/isq74ek5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fisq74ek5&h=87d34845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫唔上濾水器，不過聲稱係用吸附原理吸走氯氣。常見於沖涼濾水器同花灑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完呢三種物料，邊一種最好呢？<br />\n<br />\n從來冇最好，只有最適合。跟住就會講下點樣簡濾水器。<br />\n<br />\n簡單既次序：效能&gt;價錢&gt;處理量&gt;呎吋&gt;牌子外表<br />\n<br />\n效能：<br />\n<br />\n任你吹到幾大幾好，我地只睇一樣野：NSF認證<br />\n<br />\n因為市面有太多紅衫扮東星，所以NSF作為第三方既LAB，就可以提供一個公平既標準。如果一隻濾水器可以拎到NSF42,53認證，就代表佢係有一定效，可買。但注意一點，必須確保佢係「拎到」。因為有公司會用NSF個標準去試自己部機，然後同你講「可達NSF標準」。<br />\n<br />\n價錢：<br />\n<br />\n有錢佬請直接PASS，我地都係普通人。濾水器有平有貴，幾十蚊到幾萬蚊都有，點去簡呢？打開銀包望望，同埋睇上一點。PASS到既先再諗落去，如果上一點都唔PASS既，唔洗落去喇。<br />\n<br />\n處理量：<br />\n<br />\n一般濾水器由1千升到4,5千升都有，但冇一個標準。你一家四口我一家十二口，點同呢？但一般黎講，一家三口一日兩餐，千零升都夠做。當然啦，買大左都冇問題既，哂錢姐。<br />\n<br />\n呎吋：<br />\n<br />\n處理量愈大效能愈好，機身就愈大。如果唔係真係逼到爆既，唔需要太注意。但盡可能避免水龍頭式，因為效能未必會達標。<br />\n<br />\n牌子外形：<br />\n<br />\n裝得濾水器都係想D水乾淨姐，無謂比多錢啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇完喇，有問過我你用緊既濾水器如何既巴打，你明點解我咁答啦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b179cd390e0cb73adb3cac1afe28032529986ac","tid":230519,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:11:59.000Z","msg":"RO應該係最有效？"},{"pid":"928144968abbd0f4fc8f5c435ea72927015de848","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:21:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>RO應該係最有效？</blockquote><br />\n就過濾效能黎講，係。<br />\n但同時要考慮價錢，維修保養，實用性。同埋睇人體係咪適合長飲純水。"},{"pid":"35d04f8b50ea383a358006693d2e2dbb4da1389e","tid":230519,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:24:02.000Z","msg":"用緊doulton<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226ecd889f6516649d0d8505dcad9113a8d87926","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊doulton<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n提你樣野，定期刷濾芯唔等於延長壽命，到期一樣要換。<br />\n有幾個巴打都誤會過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d731ef8654a3ce710be58fb4f7533b5ec17a4a","tid":230519,"uid":52354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:32:12.000Z","msg":"原本用緊philips水龍頭式濾水器，而家訂左pur FM9400-B係唔係好d?"},{"pid":"5b1d5278faef707eb36608981c56ac64bfbb80a5","tid":230519,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:37:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊doulton<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n提你樣野，定期刷濾芯唔等於延長壽命，到期一樣要換。<br />\n有幾個巴打都誤會過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我會定期換一次支芯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fb8409c7b41dcbed3d5225747ede566743e170e","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:40:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原本用緊philips水龍頭式濾水器，而家訂左pur FM9400-B係唔係好d?</blockquote><br />\n好好多，但要注意，買定多D芯勤D換芯。<br />\n呢隻我印中處理量得3位數，好快飽和。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da1d3206dd8f49854a7e656a030c80cc2db8a0d9","tid":230519,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:33:12.000Z","msg":"3M同道記，兩隻都有NSF 42，51cert,邊隻好？ 3m冇得洗係咪冇咁耐用？"},{"pid":"005e41400e44a948edbb5ae5f8ecaebf70c2f542","tid":230519,"uid":12446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:39:10.000Z","msg":"我住陳年村屋，d 水喉實在勁污糟，所有水龍頭都要裝濾水先敢用，好重皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4a5ee0519ca9e53d6b17e8c2b0ab1762f4f3f7","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:48:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我住陳年村屋，d 水喉實在勁污糟，所有水龍頭都要裝濾水先敢用，好重皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搬屋！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n。。。。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ce04e49973eea3a084a4ab203b4f0bb4ae07a2","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3M同道記，兩隻都有NSF 42，51cert,邊隻好？ 3m冇得洗係咪冇咁耐用？</blockquote><br />\n首先要紏正你一個想法。<br />\n每個濾水器既濾芯都有設計壽命，一般係6,9,12個月。有得洗絕對唔等同壽命長。就算有冇得洗，都要跟番個設計壽命換芯。<br />\n道記設計壽命長D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f8e92e2d52f46e611488fc764344bb6a0e6127e","tid":230519,"uid":37343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:55:28.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"bb256d0379a45976528ff35e792acc367c49fd82","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"真係咁想我淨係拆呃人既機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁想睇我比人淋紅油？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打有電解水機唔要，可以捐比我拆，下次就同你地睇呃人之最電解水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n回報係有機睇我比人淋紅油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f500a5d2ed7d30c98b3acd25f470e7b2ef540c","tid":230519,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:03:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>3M同道記，兩隻都有NSF 42，51cert,邊隻好？ 3m冇得洗係咪冇咁耐用？</blockquote><br />\n首先要紏正你一個想法。<br />\n每個濾水器既濾芯都有設計壽命，一般係6,9,12個月。有得洗絕對唔等同壽命長。就算有冇得洗，都要跟番個設計壽命換芯。<br />\n道記設計壽命長D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用緊道記雙芯，第2隻芯係咩鋁離子，個舊野有冇用？"},{"pid":"122a8cf38107715d4591e180a288f72f82eeda46","tid":230519,"uid":14980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊doulton<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n提你樣野，定期刷濾芯唔等於延長壽命，到期一樣要換。<br />\n有幾個巴打都誤會過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n父母堅持洗就得 有一年未換過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc26d421ec28a78cae6cd80cebd2dc6a835fb50c","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T14:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>3M同道記，兩隻都有NSF 42，51cert,邊隻好？ 3m冇得洗係咪冇咁耐用？</blockquote><br />\n首先要紏正你一個想法。<br />\n每個濾水器既濾芯都有設計壽命，一般係6,9,12個月。有得洗絕對唔等同壽命長。就算有冇得洗，都要跟番個設計壽命換芯。<br />\n道記設計壽命長D<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我用緊道記雙芯，第2隻芯係咩鋁離子，個舊野有冇用？</blockquote><br />\n銀離子？銀離子用黎抗菌既，但唔會成支都係，銀離子會混入濾芯入面。所以隔離公司貨冇太深研究，成正道頓唔差得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973a5bdc08c0b545f3c90a55789684d7f8dc3766","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71bc9c92c85b759bb305a35a9320fa13c1382ebb","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:02:46.000Z","msg":"唔。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c65ebccbdfd6d55d0c66a658b54429567e544a29","tid":230519,"uid":14055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T16:14:04.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打咁詳盡嘅解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用緊道頓，買咗兩年換過1次芯，<br />\n依巴打講，佢嘅原理係用密度阻隔細菌，<br />\n我有間唔中洗濾芯，係咪洗得多會減少密度所以要換芯？"},{"pid":"3081184ab073f4f46b38d2cbbedfc36356218b15","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T03:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝巴打咁詳盡嘅解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n用緊道頓，買咗兩年換過1次芯，<br />\n依巴打講，佢嘅原理係用密度阻隔細菌，<br />\n我有間唔中洗濾芯，係咪洗得多會減少密度所以要換芯？</blockquote><br />\n係。再加上佢係有設計壽命。所以同洗唔洗冇太大關係"},{"pid":"2c526d9e8169e2198b5629b49b7505636ebd3420","tid":230519,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"紫外線又點睇"},{"pid":"e160fddc77e4e59b66a6f68dd738f5daa2242d1a","tid":230519,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T04:57:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紫外線又點睇</blockquote><br />\n你隻杯冇菌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06fb276f3b65b662e90b6765895550da80989cf","tid":230519,"uid":13355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:06:11.000Z","msg":"用緊飛利普五重過瀘，ok嗎？<br />\n租間屋成30年樓，全部水喉開出黎長期黃色。"},{"pid":"6c291259c494f1536a62f8f31188b4f0e7e42242","tid":230519,"uid":91835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T08:52:07.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻阻大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行過路過入黎睇下啦喂</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">繼指大後又一垃圾學店</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n（各位DSE雞唔該入一入黎）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/224550/page/7?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/224550/page/7?ref=ios</a>"}]}